{"tid":2259441,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美企供應鏈勢續遷出中國","createTime":"2020-10-27T00:04:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-30T01:30:42.000Z","uid":141151,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"92e29dc2fac793482745fbd025192bfc07122467","tid":2259441,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T00:04:18.000Z","msg":"美企供應鏈勢續遷出中國<br />\n<br />\nSource: 方向報<br />\n<br />\n作為全球供應鏈樞紐的中國或會面臨外國企業遷徙潮，羅兵咸永道（PwC）美國主席Tim Ryan表示，無論下月的美國總統大選結果如何，美國企業都會持續把供應鏈遷出內地，而東南亞國家、墨西哥和美國本身可望因而受惠。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>拜登發動貿戰風險較低<br />\n</strong><br />\n美國總統特朗普呼籲美企回美生產，減少對內地的依賴。他指出，PwC向578名美國企業主管作出調查，顯示在特朗普發動中美貿易戰後，美國企業把供應鏈撤離內地成了企業界的焦點話題，而在疫情爆發後，供應鏈風險議題的重要性有增無減，更已提升到董事會層級，並形容目前供應鏈集中於內地的程度屬「前所未見」。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">該調查顯示，約46%的受訪美企主管表示，「強烈同意」美國政府應提高必要產品在美國的產能，以提振美國經濟。另外，近三成受訪者表示，「強烈同意」無論誰入主白宮，對內地設下的貿易限制都會持續增加。但Ryan表示，研究發現，擔心特朗普主政帶來貿易戰風險的受訪主管，略多於擔憂拜登執政。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n他又指，企業必然會繼續投資內地這個大市場，但與以往相比，確實有更多美國企業計劃分散投資，料此趨勢未來幾年仍將持續。"},{"pid":"4dbdb117e429de84140a24f82ca02effa4e7a5bf","tid":2259441,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T00:27:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efcf73560429e30db291732964712c4cdc6b3f69","tid":2259441,"uid":292497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T01:17:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"802b5725f61abc51719c1ec71e75be523351c64d","tid":2259441,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T01:21:44.000Z","msg":"方向報認證拜燈奶共<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c97a0e99ce843d377115269291235eb6a16696b9","tid":2259441,"uid":355748,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T01:50:24.000Z","msg":"生意佬理撚得你<br />\n拜登上照樣走人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64f7746773b73bd95184ab786d3ba28d1ce13ba9","tid":2259441,"uid":26424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T02:00:22.000Z","msg":"遷左10年 越遷貿易逆差越高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"373722043c6f854a41dba1a9f0be7028832dd76f","tid":2259441,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T00:19:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9581fe977acf1ffd7dff2856597518d22ddf880a","tid":2259441,"uid":51820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T01:30:42.000Z","msg":"推"}]}